<description>

A new share account is created from the Client Detail page. The Share Account Application form contains Share Product dropdown (selecting a product auto-populates default values), Submitted On date, Requested Shares (bounded by product min/max per client), Application Date, Savings Account for Charges dropdown (lists the client's active savings accounts to debit fees from), External ID, and a Charges section. Clicking "Submit" creates the account in "Submitted and Pending Approval" status.

The Share Account Detail page displays the share account number, product name, client name, status badge, total approved shares, total pending shares, and unit price. Action buttons change based on status: Pending offers Approve (with Approved Shares and Approved Date) and Reject; Approved offers Activate and Undo Approval; Active offers Apply Additional Shares (purchase more shares), Redeem Shares (redemption amount is calculated as shares multiplied by current unit price and credited to the linked savings account), and Close. Tabs show Purchased Shares (table with Date, Type, Number of Shares, Unit Price, Amount, and Status), Dividends (posted dividend distributions with Date, Amount Per Share, and Total Amount), and Charges.

---


</description>

<workflows>
WF-001 | Submit Share Account Application | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Submit | on_success: creates account in Submitted and Pending Approval status
WF-002 | Approve Share Account Application | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Submitted and Pending Approval | terminal: Approve | on_success: changes status to Approved
WF-003 | Reject Share Account Application | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Submitted and Pending Approval | terminal: Reject | on_success: marks application as Rejected
WF-004 | Activate Approved Share Account | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Approved | terminal: Activate | on_success: changes status to Active
WF-005 | Undo Approval | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Approved | terminal: Undo Approval | on_success: reverts status to Submitted and Pending Approval
WF-006 | Apply Additional Shares (Active Account) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Apply Additional Shares | on_success: initiates purchase of additional shares
WF-007 | Redeem Shares (Active Account) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Redeem Shares | on_success: credits calculated redemption amount to selected savings account
WF-008 | Close Share Account (Active Account) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Close | on_success: closes account (status -> Closed)
</workflows>

